“A-seng5, li2 u7 khoaN3-kiN3 bo5?  Hia chit8 keng chhu3 e5 goa7-bin7, khng3 kui-tui e5 mih8-kiaN7, u7 chit8 e5 lang5 phah-piaN3 teh se2 thang-a2.  Hah!  Hah!  Chin ho2 chhio3, goa2 m7-bat khoaN3-tioh8 chit khoan2 e5 lang5.”  “Si7 an2-choaN2, si7 sim2-mih8 tai7-chi3?  Si7 lang5 si2--khi3?  A2-si7 u7 lang5 poaN lai5?”  A-seng5 mng7 “Goa2 m7 chai, ho2, lan2 lai5 khi3 khoaN3 mai7, lai5 mng7 khoaN3-mai7.”  Chit 2 e5 sio2 peng5-iu2 chiu7 koaN2-kin2 chau2-khi3 khoaN3.  In si7 chha-put-to 10 hoe3 e5 gin2-na2, in-ui7 ka-teng5 khun3-khou2, sou2-i2 seng-khu san2-san2.  Kau3-ui7 A-seng5 chiu7 mng7 hit-e5 lang5 “A-peh ah, li2 ti7 chia teh cho3 sim2-mih8?  Li2 beh poaN lai5 chia si7 bo5?  Li2 thai3 e7 chhit kau3 hiah chheng-khi3, si7 beh cho3 nau7-jiat8 si7 bo5?  E-hng kiam2 u7 beh pang3 phau3?”   
Chhit thang-a2 e5 Lou5 sian-siN ai3 chhio3 kong2 “Lai5!  Lai5!  Sio2 peng5-iu2, kong2 khah ban7 leh, li2 mng7 chiah choe7 e5 bun7-te5, hun-khui lai5 mng7 khah ho2.  Si7 lah, goa2 tu2-tu2 poaN lai5 chia, bin5-a2-am3 goan2 ti7 chia u7 beh chhiuN3-koa, lin2 chiah long2 chhoa7 lai5!  Lin2 ia7 thang chhoa7 peng5-iu2 lai5, ia7 chhoa7 lin2 pa-pa ma-ma lai5, goa2 beh ka3 lin2 chhiuN3 chin ho2 thiaN e5 koa.”  
“Li2 beh ka3 goan2 chhiuN3 sim2-mih8 koa?  Si7 kok8-kok8 ke, a2-si7 gu5 poah8-loh8 chui2, goan2 long2 chin ai3 chhiuN3 chit 2 tiau5 koa”.  
“M7-si7, goa2 beh ka3 lin2 chhiuN3 koan-he7 Ia5-sou e5 koa, chin ho2 thiaN, lin2 tek-khak chin ai3 chhiuN3.”  
“Ho2, a-peh ah, goan2 bin5-a2-am3 chiah lai5, goan2 beh chhoa7 chin che7 lang5 lai5 ouh!”  
A-seng5 bo5 kong2 peh8-chhat8, keh-jit8 hit am3 7 tiam2-poaN3 ko2-jian5 chhoa7 20 goa7 e5 sio2 peng5-iu2 lai5, lai5 chham-ka Lou5 sian-siN e5 chu7-hoe7.  Ki5-tiong u7 chit8 e5 sio2 peng5-iu2 kio3 choe3 A-kiu5, si7 in e5 gin2-na2 tong2 e5 chong2 chi2-hui, A-seng5 chiu7 chhoa7 i khi3 che7 siong7 thau5-cheng5.  Lou5 sian-siN chiu7 pun si-koa-chip8 hou7 in, tai7-ke chiu7 chhiuN3 kau3 chin sim-sek.  In m7-bat chhiuN3 chit khoan2 e5 koa, chong2-si7 chhiuN3 kah chin toa7 siaN, thau5-cheng5 u7 chit8 tai5 hong-khim5, in long2 m7 jin7 su, chhiuN3 pi2 hong-khim5 khah toa7 siaN, na2 teh pi2-sai3.  Lou5 sian-siN chiu7 kong2 Ia5-sou e5 tai7-chi3 hou7 in thiaN, keh-jit8 A-seng5 koh chhoa7 in lai5, A-seng5 thiaN hiah-e5 to7-li2 siu7 chin toa7 e5 kam2-tong7.  I kui7-loh8 ki5-to2, kiu5 Ia5-sou sia3-bian2 i e5 choe7, i khia7 khi2-lai5 e5 si5, i e5 bin7 u7 hoaN-hi2 e5 kng, in-ui7 Chu2 Ia5-sou i2-keng tiam3 ti7 i e5 sim-lai7.  
In chhut khi3 e5 si5 A-kiu5 tui3 A-seng5 “Hah!  Li2 chin gong7, li2 ia7 beh kap lang5 sin3 Ia5-sou, ho2, li2 sin3 Ia5-sou goan2 long2 bo5 ai3 kap li2 cho3 peng5-iu2, li2 siuN7 khoaN3-mai7, mai3 sin3 si7 khah ho2.”  A-seng5 sin3 Ia5-sou, i e5 sim-lai7 u7 kong2 boe7 chhut e5 peng5-an kap hoaN-hi2.  Hian7-chai7 A-kiu5 in long2 bo5 beh kap i thit-tho5, i ia7 bo5 liah8-choe3 iau3-kin2.  Au7-lai5, A-seng5 long2 ka-ki7 chit8 e5 khi3 Lou5 sian-siN hia gian2-kiu3 Seng3-keng, Lou5 sian-siN tak8-jit8 ka7 i kou2-le7, kio3 i tioh8 thun-lun2 ui7-tioh8 Ia5-sou e5 ian5-kou3, tioh8 koe3 tek-seng3 e5 seng-oah8.  A-kiu5 tek8-piat8 chin oan3-hun7 i, mui2 pai2 A-seng5 na7 kap i kong2 khi2 Ia5-sou e5 tai7-chi3, i long2 eng7 chin chhou-siok8 e5 oe7 lai5 me7 i.
U7 chit8 le2-pai3-jit8 cha2-khi2, A-seng5 ti7 Chu2-jit8-oh8 tit-tioh8 chit8-pun2 Seng3-keng, i sim-lai7 chin hoaN-hi2, i siuN7 chin ai3 koaN2-kin2 theh8 khi3 ka7 i e5 sio2 peng5-iu2 tian2, hou7 in him-sian7 thang te3 i lai5 thak8 Chu2-jit8-oh8.  Chu2-jit8-oh8 chit8 e7 soah, A-seng5 kin2 chau2 tng2-khi3.  
“Lin2 khoaN3 goa2 u7 chit8-pun2 Seng3-keng si7 Lou5 sian-siN sang3 e5, goa2 na7 tak8-jit8 khi3, i long2 ka3 goa2 thak8 Seng3-keng, bo5 goa7 ku2 goa2 chiu7 e7 hiau2 thak8 hou7 lin2 thiaN.”  A-seng5 chin hoaN-hi2 tui3 ui5 i e5 sio2 peng5-iu2 kong2.  
A-kiu5 kong2 “Hou7 goa2 khoaN3”, chiu7 chiap Seng3-keng khi3; siuN7 be7 kau3, A-kiu5 chiong Seng3-keng e5 phoe5 thiah phoa3, au7-lai5 koh chiong Seng3-keng choan5-pun2 thiah hou7 i phoa3 kou5-kou5.  A-seng5 kim3 be7 tiau5 soah toa7 siaN hau2 chhut-lai5, na2 joe5 i e5 bak8-chiu chiu7 khi3 chhoe7 Lou5 sian-siN.  I phak ti7 Lou5 sian-siN e5 kha-thau5-u toa7 khau3, koh chiong hit-e5 keng-koe3 kong2 hou7 Lou5 sian-siN thiaN, “Lou5 sian-siN, che-si7 goa2 thau5 pai2 tit-tioh8 e5 Seng3-keng, goa2 chi2-u7 chit8 pun2, chong2-si7 hian7-chai7 bo5 khi3 lah, hou7 lang5 li3-phoa3 khi3 lah!”  “A-seng5 bo5 iau3-kin2, goa2 the3 li2 siuN7 pan7-hoat.”  
Keng-koe3 2 geh8-jit8 au7, u7 chit8-am3, A-seng5 koh tit-tioh8 chit8-pun2 Sin-iok Seng3-keng, chit pai2 i chiu7 chhang3 ti7 saN e5 lai7-te7-a2, i beh theh8 tng2-khi3 kia3 i e5 lau7-bu2 khng3.  Chong2-si7 i boe7 ki3-tit Lou5 sian-siN e5 thang-a2 chhit kau3 chin chheng-khi3, A-kiu5 kap A-kiat bih ti7 thang-a2 khau2 khoaN3 kau3 chin chheng-chho2.  A-seng5 beh tng2-khi3 e5 si5, khoaN3 goa7-khau2 si3-piN long2 bo5 lang5, chiu7 hong3-sim kiaN5, na2 chai au7-bin7 A-kiu5 kap A-kiat jip8 oa2-lai5, hoah kong2 “A-seng5, li2 hit pun2 chheh chioh khoaN3 leh!”  
“Sim2-mih8 chheh?”  A-seng5 mng7.  “Lou5 sian-siN tu2 chiah hou7 li2 hit pun2, theh8 lai5, goa2 thak8 hou7 li2 thiaN.”  “M7, goa2 m7 hou7 li2, i2-cheng5 hit pun2 hou7 li2 li3-phoa3, chit pun2 goa2 choat8-tui3 m7 hou7 lin2 khoaN3”.  A-seng5 e5 oe7 kong2 iau2-boe7 soah, A-kiu5 chiu7 eng7 kun5-thau5-bu2 loan7 cheng, A-seng5 iau2 m7-kheng2 pang3 hit pun2 Seng3-keng.  A-kiu5 khah toa7-han3 koh u7 lat8, chiu7 phah A-seng5, phah kah chin siong-tiong7, koh chiong hit pun2 Seng3-keng hiat ti7 piN-a2 chiu7 liu chau2, kong2 “Ho2, ka7 li2 ka3-si7 leh, khoaN3 li2 kaN2 koh khi3 sin3 bo5!”
Keh-jit8 cha2-khi2, A-seng5 chhiN2-khi2--lai5 khoaN3-kiN3 ka-ki7 khun3 ti7 chit8 teng2 peh8 bin5-chhng5, si3-ui5 ia7 u7 chin choe7 lang5 to2 ti7 hia teh khun3.  “Sio2 peng5-iu2, li2 u7 khun3 khi3 bo5?  Hou7 lang5 phah kau3 hiah li7-hai7, chin kho2-lin5, ...... bo5 iau3-kin2 i-seng oe7 ka7 li2 i-ho2, hian7-chai7 li2 e5 ma-ma ti7 goa7-khau2 teh tan2 li2,” chit8-ui7 jin5-chu5 e5 hou7-su7 eng7 chit8 nia2 than2-a2 ka7 i kah.  A-seng5 e5 pa-pa ma-ma jip8 lai5, che7 ti7 bin5-chhng5-piN, A-seng5 e5 ma-ma kong2 “Li2 khoaN3, kho2-ouN3 e5 A-kiu5, chiong goa2 e5 gin2-na2 phah kau3 chiah li7-hai7, bo5 iau3-kin2, A-seng5 lan2 beh kio3 keng2-chhat ka7 i liah8-khi3 koaiN.”
Lou5 sian-siN tak8-jit8 lai5 khoaN3 A-seng5, u7 chit8-jit8 i toa3 chit8-pun2 Seng3-keng lai5, tui3 A-seng5 kong2 “Hit-jit8, keng2-chhat khoaN3-kiN3 li2 to2 ti7 chit8-pun2 Seng3-keng e5 piN-a2, che chiu7-si7 cheng3-beng5 li2 ui7-tioh8 Siong7-te3 e5 oe7 siu7-khou2”.  Lou5 sian-siN hian-khui Seng3-keng thak8 hou7 i thiaN “Ui7-tioh8 Goa2, lang5 chiah loe2-me7 lin2, khun2-tiok8 lin2, hui2-pong3 lin2 ban7-hang7 e5 phaiN2, lin2 chiu7 u7 hok-khi3”.  “Lou5 sian-siN, che si7 Seng3-keng e5 oe7 a2 m7-si7?”  “Si7, A-seng5 goa2 i2-keng eng7 ang5 ian5-pit chiong hit chat e5 Seng3-keng cho3 ki3-ho7”, keng-koe3 4 jit8, A-seng5 oe7 khi2 lai5 che7 lah, i hian-khui Seng3-keng, koh khoaN3-kiN3 leng7-goa7 chit8 chat chiu7-si7 Lou5 sian-siN ka7 i cho3 ki3-ho7 e5, chiu7-si7 “Tui3-tek8 lin2 e5 tioh8 thiaN3 in, oan3-hun7 lin2 e5, tioh8 ho2 khoan2-thai7 in, loe2-me7 lin2 e5, tioh8 ka7 in chiok-hok, leng5-jiok8 lin2 e5, tioh8 thoe3 in ki5-to2”. A-seng5 thak8 liau2 chiu7 siuN7 kong2, ma-ma na7 u7-iaN2 kio3 keng2-chhat liah8 A-kiu5 khi3 koaiN, an2-ni chiu7 bo5 thiaN3 tui3-tek8, i koh thak8 kui2-na7-pai2, chiu7 the3 A-kiu5 ki5-to2.
A-seng5 e5 siong-jiah chiam7-chiam7 ho2 khi2--lai5 lah.  I e5 pa-pa chiu7 chhoa7 i tng2-khi3, hit am3 A-kiu5 lai5 i e5 chhu3 ka7 A-seng5 kong2, “A-seng5, tui3 goa2 ka7 li2 phah liau2-au7, goa2 e5 sim chin kan-khou2 boe7 chiah8 png7, boe7 khun3--tit, goa2 chin hou7-hoe2 goa2 sou2 cho3 e5, A-seng5 chhiaN2 li2 sia3-bian2 goa2?”  A-seng5 khoaN3-kiN3 m7-bat khau3 e5 A-kiu5 teh lau5 bak8-sai2.  A-seng5 chiu7 hian-khui Seng3-keng thak8 hou7 A-kiu5 thiaN “Na7-si7 Goa2 ka7 lin2 kong2, tui3-tek8 lin2 e5, tioh8 thiaN3 in”.  “A-kiu5, chit pun2 Seng3-keng kio3 goa2 thiaN3 li2, ui7 li2 ki5-to2.  Pun2-lai5, goa2 si7 boe7 oe7 thiaN3 li2, in-ui7 li2 ka7 goa2 li3-phoa3 1 pun2 Seng3-keng, chong2-si7 chit pun2 Seng3-keng kio3 goa2 ui7 Ia5-sou e5 ian5-kou3 thiaN3 li2, sou2-i2 goa2 hoaN-hi2 sia3-bian2 li2”.  A-kiu5 chhiu2 chi2 hit pun2 Seng3-keng kong2 “Si7, chit pun2 Seng3-keng e5 oe7 kai2-pian3 goa2 e5 sim, A-seng5 li2 na7 beh khi3 Chu2-jit8-oh8, goa2 chiah kap li2 lai5 khi3, goa2 ia7 kap li2 lai5 khi3 sin3 Ia5-sou.”
(Ka-teng5 e5 peng5-iu2 te7 58 ki5, 1962 ni5 12 geh8)
